benchmark_config.jira_title: Implement/Test API: DELETE /1.0/kb/bundles/{bundleId}/customFields - Remove custom fields from bundle

covered: Valid Deletion: Scenarios cover successful removal of custom fields under various conditions (TC01-05, TC10, TC11, TC15, TC20, TC21).
Non-Existent Resource: TC07 covers deletion of a non-existent bundle.
Concurrency: TC16 covers concurrent deletion requests for the same bundle.
Authorization: TC08 and TC13 cover missing header and invalid token scenarios.
gaps: Soft Deletes: No test covers soft deletion behavior if the API supports it.
Rate Limiting: No test covers rate limiting by sending multiple requests in a short time.
GET/POST/PUT/PATCH guidelines: These tests do not cover guidelines for other HTTP methods.
Caching Behavior: No tests verify caching headers for DELETE responses.
Pagination: No tests cover pagination handling for large datasets (not directly relevant to DELETE but part of guidelines).
recommendations: Add a test to verify soft delete behavior if applicable.
Add a rate limiting test by sending multiple DELETE requests in quick succession.
Add tests for GET/POST/PUT/PATCH guidelines if the API includes those endpoints.
Add tests to verify caching headers (ETag, Cache-Control) for DELETE responses.
Add pagination tests for listing custom fields if the API supports pagination.
